Package: cmad

URL:
	http://cern.ch/mad

Build:
  see lib/makefile or...

  ...run the makefile contained in the mad folder:
  MacOSX:
  	make macosx LIBNAME=libmad-OSX.so

  Linux:
  	make linux LIBNAME=libmad-Linux.so

  Windows: (NYI)
  	make windows LIBNAME=libmad-Windows.dll

Cleaning:
  make -C cmad clean

Usage:
  local oss  = jit.os
  local ffi  = require 'ffi'
  local cmad = ffi.load("lib/cmad/libcmad-" .. oss .. ".so")